Package: pared2026v1
Type: Package
Title: Pareto-Based Regularization and Multi-Objective Tuning
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Priyam Das
Maintainer: Priyam Das <dasp4@vcu.edu>
Description: Provides Pareto-based multi-objective tuning tools for regularized
    statistical models, including elastic net, fused lasso, and joint graphical
    lasso examples. The package also includes a general-purpose Pareto optimizer
    for user-defined objective functions and visualization tools for two- and
    three-dimensional Pareto fronts.
